room_title: Escape room "The Great Eureka Springs Bank Heist" by Escape Room 13 in Eureka Springs
room_address: 13 N Main St Eureka Springs, AR 72632
room_description: It all started in September of 1922 when five men camped in the woods of Leatherwood Creek. These men made plans to rob the bank in Eureka Springs. One of them, the driver, who was not a seasoned bank robber, had no business being there. Or did he? Help his family by going back to 1922 and try to find evidence of his innocence.
